  <brief_title>Effects of Allium Hookeri on Blood Glucose</brief_title>
  <official_title>An 8 Week, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Crossover Clinical Trial of Allium Hookeri Root Extract on Anti-diabetic Effects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
